author: gartung
body: Unused getParamDumper checker requires a change to evalCall parameters in llvm/clang 9 in order to be registered. The text file produced was never used for anything. Unregistering the checker rather than removing it because it still compiles. It can be fixed at a later time if there is interest.
title: Utilities/StaticAnalysers: Unregister unused getParamDumper checker
